{"tid":245153,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"老友跳樓死左，我真係接受唔到","createTime":"2017-05-16T04:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T13:23:51.000Z","uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92b7ea10e6aec33ebf5d1fbe0df2737acd0442f2","tid":245153,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"從朋友身邊得知到依個訊息都嚇左一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明前幾日先出黎一齊食飯聚舊 傾得開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點會估到你今日就走左 咁就無左個由中學玩到依家嘅老友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家做乜都無晒心情<br />\n粒聲唔出走去跳樓 我地當中都無人知咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係知無左個老友"},{"pid":"54137d0a201221be8e249f766827f166620406c5","tid":245153,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"你同佢都幾老友喎&hellip;<br />\n不過點解跳就冇人知嘅，唔好諗太多"},{"pid":"4a04d8939533711818ebef918eb0963d77b6e30a","tid":245153,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"我都試過，好自責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b6030ec4e7fbe6baec542c99a8596cc78aed23","tid":245153,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你同佢都幾老友喎&hellip;<br />\n不過點解跳就冇人知嘅，唔好諗太多</blockquote><br />\n咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919a9ca47b93e124159b49383c566119f826652e","tid":245153,"uid":40389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"我諗 你當佢朋友 佢無當你係朋友"},{"pid":"4d9d7785da9125ccee7fe67067046fa9171500fa","tid":245153,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗 你當佢朋友 佢無當你係朋友</blockquote><br />\n點解"},{"pid":"692953d7ced638e81d7ff4b4e0d64909deb9cbb0","tid":245153,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"你同佢都幾老友喎&hellip;"},{"pid":"4d256afc98eff3b658d27dc30149a18eb3b01241","tid":245153,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:42:50.000Z","msg":"做乜野 咪話左無人知點解跳 前前後後都無任何因素可以比我地察覺到佢有咩唔妥 點知佢話走就走 連佢屋企都估唔到"},{"pid":"2f97f2474c22fd7468a63ac5863b400a9bae9208","tid":245153,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:47:48.000Z","msg":"藍鯨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fafa429c13e95d5c96885dd0125e89d5f46a75","tid":245153,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:50:25.000Z","msg":"前排都有個中學時期幾fd既朋友跳左樓 <br />\n知道消息之後心情真係唔知想點"},{"pid":"9f5f950ec755438a0e8a5e62074e2ff69725fed7","tid":245153,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"我見完我老友上佢屋企食完飯,<br />\n<br />\n第二日佢跳左落黎,<br />\n<br />\n都兩三年了...<br />\n<br />\n佢有情緒病,入過精神病院"},{"pid":"3fdcda20208ec6c451725b38ac7cc48b99d4e038","tid":245153,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"有無諗過他殺？"},{"pid":"cde20624408ed242d19c8044fb0f7e0735b16f44","tid":245153,"uid":99259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從朋友身邊得知到依個訊息都嚇左一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明前幾日先出黎一齊食飯聚舊 傾得開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點會估到你今日就走左 咁就無左個由中學玩到依家嘅老友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家做乜都無晒心情<br />\n粒聲唔出走去跳樓 我地當中都無人知咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係知無左個老友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽到呢個消息真係好心up..巴打你而家見點啊? 最近我都有個朋友佢伴侶唔係到, 我聽到都有啲失落"},{"pid":"595dbde4b8488408df99460878a1d20cf49c6b34","tid":245153,"uid":68098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"別太自責<br />\n佢選擇左呢一條路<br />\n唔係三言兩語可以改變到佢既決定<br />\n睇下佢親人果邊有無野可以幫到手"},{"pid":"eec144d77b41667d3439a7b4b2ce1036ab083b12","tid":245153,"uid":106045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T09:55:15.000Z","msg":"有好多時佢地已經唔係第一次諗過自殺架喇，想當年前一晚仲一家人開開心心食完飯第二朝就有親人跳樓死左"},{"pid":"e10cca2ee1ba1dd63fa1cd88777259f2c6fc652c","tid":245153,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樓主一樣經歷<br />\n<br />\n完全冇任何蹟象，平時係開心果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好後悔冇陪佢多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045cb5350ea2dabe27878283c0a60d3ad93c97e4","tid":245153,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbde9d8873e8c91638eb39f2dab0cda92b750a8d","tid":245153,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:23:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}